Ryan Aviation
-
Abu Dhabi
Ryan Aviation on behalf of our client Jet Airways, with bases in Abu Dhabi, New York, Istanbul and Mumbai, are seeking B777 Captains / Instructors / Examiners, current and qualified on the B777.
Positions are available for an immediate start, subject to assessment and Indian DGCA Security Clearance. Flights & hotel for assessment provided by the Airline.
THE AIRLINE WILL COVER COST OF EXPENSES INVOLVED IN UNDERGOING RECENCY TRAINING for B777 Captains who have not flown for more than 1 year subject to certain conditions.
Basic salary and overtime allowance Accommodation allowance 6 weeks on 2 weeks off Travel allowance Medical cover Loss of license cover Personal accident cover Transport provided
JAA/ICAO/FAA license types are acceptable
Candidate's requirements:
Have a current & valid B777 type rating Min 6000 hours total flying time of which at least 2500 hours PIC & 700 hours should be on type Last flight on type within 36 months Hold a first class medical certificate No history of incidents or accidents
